{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"जब सूर्य लपेट दिया जाएगा।","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā al-shamsu kuwwirat ","translations":["When","the sun","is wrapped up","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","al-shamsu","kuwwirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,1290],[3,1290,2355]]}},{"name":"81:2","price":"और जब सितारे प्रकाश रहित हो जाएँगे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-nujūmu inkadarat ","translations":["And when","the stars","fall, losing their luster","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-nujūmu","inkadarat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,2060],[3,2060,3665]]}},{"name":"81:3","price":"और जब पर्वत चलाए जाएँगे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jibālu suyyirat ","translations":["And when","the mountains","are moved away","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jibālu","suyyirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1670],[3,1670,2705]]}},{"name":"81:4","price":"और जब गाभिन ऊँटनियाँ छोड़ दी जाएँगी।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-ʿishāru ʿuṭṭilat ","translations":["And when","the full-term she-camels","(are) left untended","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-ʿishāru","ʿuṭṭilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,1850],[3,1850,2775]]}},{"name":"81:5","price":"और जब जंगली जानवर एकत्रित किए जाएँगे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-wuḥūshu ḥushirat ","translations":["And when","the wild beasts","are gathered","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-wuḥūshu","ḥushirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1770],[3,1770,2535]]}},{"name":"81:6","price":"और जब सागर भड़काए जाएँगे।[1]","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-6) इनमें प्रलय के प्रथम चरण में ब्रह्मांड में जो उथल-पुथल होगी, उसको दिखाया गया है कि आकाश, धरती और पर्वत, सागर तथा जीव जंतुओं की क्या दशा होगी। और माया मोह में पड़ा इनसान इसी संसार में अपने प्रियवर धन से कैसा बेपरवाह हो जाएगा। वन पशु भी भय के मारे एकत्र हो जाएँगे। सागरों के जल-प्लावन से धरती पर जल ही जल दिखाई देगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-biḥāru sujjirat ","translations":["And when","the seas","are made to overflow","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-biḥāru","sujjirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,1730],[3,1730,2795]]}},{"name":"81:7","price":"और जब प्राण मिला दिए जाएँगे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-nufūsu zuwwijat ","translations":["And when","the souls","are paired","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-nufūsu","zuwwijat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,1980],[3,1980,3065]]}},{"name":"81:8","price":"और जब जीवित गाड़ी गई लड़की से पूछा जाएगा।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-mawūdatu su-ilat ","translations":["And when","the female infant buried alive","is asked","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-mawūdatu","su-ilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,2070],[3,2070,2955]]}},{"name":"81:9","price":"कि वह किस अपराध के कारण मारी गई?","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-ayyi dhanbin qutilat ","translations":["For what","sin","she was killed","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-ayyi","dhanbin","qutilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2670],[3,2670,4175]]}},{"name":"81:10","price":"तथा जब कर्मपत्र (आमाल नामे) फैला दिए जाएँगे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-ṣuḥufu nushirat ","translations":["And when","the pages","are laid open","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-ṣuḥufu","nushirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1360],[3,1360,2195]]}},{"name":"81:11","price":"और जब आकाश उधेड़ दिया जाएगा।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-samāu kushiṭat ","translations":["And when","the sky","is stripped away","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-samāu","kushiṭat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,2980],[3,2980,3775]]}},{"name":"81:12","price":"और जब जहन्नम दहकाई जाएगी।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jaḥīmu suʿʿirat ","translations":["And when","the Hellfire","is set ablaze","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jaḥīmu","suʿʿirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,730],[2,730,1710],[3,1710,2735]]}},{"name":"81:13","price":"और जब जन्नत क़रीब लाई जाएगी।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-janatu uz'lifat ","translations":["And when","Paradise","is brought near","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-janatu","uz'lifat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,2230],[3,2230,3695]]}},{"name":"81:14","price":"तो प्रत्येक प्राणी जान लेगा कि वह क्या लेकर आया है।[2]","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (7-14) इन आयतों में प्रलय के दूसरे चरण की दशा को दर्शाया गया है कि इनसानों की आस्था और कर्मों के अनुसार श्रेणियाँ बनेंगी। नृशंसितों (मज़लूमों) के साथ न्याय किया जाएगा। कर्म-पत्र खोल दिए जाएँगे। नरक भड़काई जाएगी। स्वर्ग सामने कर दिया जाएगा। और उस समय सभी को वास्तविकता का ज्ञान हो जाएगा। इस्लाम के उदय के समय अरब में कुछ लोग पुत्रियों को जन्म लेते ही जीवित गाड़ दिया करते थे। इस्लाम ने नारियों को जीवन प्रदान किया। और उन्हें जीवित गाड़ देने को घोर अपराध घोषित किया। आयत संख्या 8 में उन्हीं नृशंस अपराधियों को धिक्कारा गया है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalimat nafsun mā aḥḍarat ","translations":["Will know","a soul","what","it has brought","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalimat","nafsun","mā","aḥḍarat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1610],[3,1610,3450],[4,3450,5015]]}},{"name":"81:15","price":"मैं क़सम खाता हूँ पीछे हटने वाले सितारों की।","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu bil-khunasi ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by the retreating planets","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","bil-khunasi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,3350],[3,3350,5775]]}},{"name":"81:16","price":"चलने वाले, छिप जाने वाले तारों की।","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"al-jawāri al-kunasi ","translations":["Those that run","(and) disappear","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["al-jawāri","al-kunasi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,3575]]}},{"name":"81:17","price":"और रात की (क़सम), जब वह आती और जाती है।","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā ʿasʿasa ","translations":["And the night","when","it departs","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","ʿasʿasa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1720],[3,1720,2895]]}},{"name":"81:18","price":"तथा सुबह की, जब वह रौशन होने लगे।","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ṣub'ḥi idhā tanaffasa ","translations":["And the dawn","when","it breathes","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ṣub'ḥi","idhā","tanaffasa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,1680],[3,1680,3185]]}},{"name":"81:19","price":"निःसंदेह यह (क़ुरआन) एक आदरणीय संदेशवाहक की लाई हुई वाणी है।","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu laqawlu rasūlin karīmin ","translations":["Indeed, it","(is) surely a word","(of) a Messenger","noble","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","laqawlu","rasūlin","karīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1610],[2,1610,2520],[3,2520,3670],[4,3670,5985]]}},{"name":"81:20","price":"जो शक्तिशाली है, अर्श (सिंहासन) वाले के पास उच्च पद वाला है।","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"dhī quwwatin ʿinda dhī al-ʿarshi makīnin ","translations":["Possessor of","power","with","(the) Owner of","the Throne","secure","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["dhī","quwwatin","ʿinda","dhī","al-ʿarshi","makīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,1460],[3,1460,2430],[4,2430,2580],[5,2580,3460],[6,3460,5415]]}},{"name":"81:21","price":"उसकी वहाँ (आसमानों में) बात मानी जाती है और बड़ा विश्वसनीय है।[3]","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (15-21) तारों की व्यवस्था गति तथा अँधेरे के पश्चात् नियमित रूप से उजाला की शपथ इस बात की गवाही है कि क़ुरआन ज्योतिष की बकवास नहीं। बल्कि यह ईश-वाणी है। जिसको एक शक्तिशाली तथा सम्मान वाला फ़रिश्ता लेकर मुह़म्मद सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम के पास आया। और अमानतदारी से इसे पहुँचाया।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"muṭāʿin thamma amīnin ","translations":["One to be obeyed","and","trustworthy","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["muṭāʿin","thamma","amīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,2760],[3,2760,4885]]}},{"name":"81:22","price":"और तुम्हारा साथी कोई दीवाना नहीं हैं।","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ṣāḥibukum bimajnūnin ","translations":["And not","(is) your companion","mad","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ṣāḥibukum","bimajnūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,2470],[3,2470,5065]]}},{"name":"81:23","price":"और निश्चय उन्होंने उस (जिबरील) को स्पष्ट क्षितिज पर देखा है।","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walaqad raāhu bil-ufuqi al-mubīni ","translations":["And certainly","he saw him","in the horizon","the clear","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["walaqad","raāhu","bil-ufuqi","al-mubīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1710],[3,1710,2760],[4,2760,5235]]}},{"name":"81:24","price":"और वह परोक्ष (ग़ैब) की बातें बताने में कृपण नहीं हैं।[4]","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4. (22-24) इनमें यह चेतावनी दी गई है कि महा ईशदूत (मुह़म्मद सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) जो सुना रहे हैं, और जो फ़रिश्ता वह़्य (प्रकाशना) लाता है, उन्होंने उसे देखा है। वह परोक्ष की बातें प्रस्तुत कर रहे हैं, कोई ज्योतिष की बात नहीं, जो धिक्कारे शौतान ज्योतिषियों को दिया करते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa ʿalā al-ghaybi biḍanīnin ","translations":["And not","he (is)","on","the unseen","a withholder","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","ʿalā","al-ghaybi","biḍanīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,940],[3,940,1420],[4,1420,2330],[5,2330,5085]]}},{"name":"81:25","price":"और यह (क़ुरआन) किसी धिक्कारे हुए शैतान की वाणी नहीं है।","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa biqawli shayṭānin rajīmin ","translations":["And not","it","(is the) word","(of) Shaitaan","accursed","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","biqawli","shayṭānin","rajīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1010],[3,1010,1800],[4,1800,2620],[5,2620,3765]]}},{"name":"81:26","price":"फिर तुम कहाँ जा रहे हो?","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ayna tadhhabūna ","translations":["So where","are you going","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ayna","tadhhabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,3155]]}},{"name":"81:27","price":"यह तो समस्त संसार वालों के लिए एक उपदेश है।","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"i